{"tid":370719,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天鴿襲港】颱風橫掃澳門 最少3死兩失蹤","createTime":"2017-08-23T07:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T07:39:14.000Z","uid":81602,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e1e4bcda449c61df6babb4e6e7a0067e94a11ec","tid":370719,"uid":81602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:36:51.000Z","msg":"天鴿橫掃澳門，不但造成斷水斷電，並釀成傷亡。澳門民防行動中心表示，截至下午2時15分，最少造成3人死亡，其中一名為62歲本地男子從高處墮下身亡；另一名45歲支那男遊客則遭重型車輛輾斃，車輛更疑不顧而去；另一名30歲持本地藍咭男外傭，則遭強風吹倒撞牆，送院經搶救後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n另外，今早於筷子基雅典灣附近，有4人一度失踪，最終只有2人獲救，其餘至今仍2人失蹤；中午時分，內港一艘停泊於澳門的漁船亦沉沒，當局正在跟進中。<br />\n民防行動中心表示，暫時分別在澳門和離島錄得154宗事故報告，包括17宗石屎脫落及墮下；33宗招牌廣告、簷篷、鐵片/鐵枝、窗墜落及搖搖欲墜；5宗棚架欲墜及倒塌；38宗天線及樹木倒塌；16宗電梯被困事故。民防行動中心呼籲市民於颱風期間留在家中，如非必要勿外出，免生意外。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170823/57117272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170823%2F57117272&d=MZbb6wOW8NUOP6KiUv6%2B8FzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=65f31ee6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170823%2F57117272&h=bd71fbb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170823/57117272</a>"},{"pid":"a161d02ab1f6e4bc205618de9440557d7ea20b07","tid":370719,"uid":81602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170823/large/1503472463_6c7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170823%2Flarge%2F1503472463_6c7e.jpg&h=ed5e378b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48ce4344a26a17e461471d25321a67cfdcb675a8","tid":370719,"uid":81602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:38:16.000Z","msg":"支那畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class